 68	|--------|------|---------|-------------|
 69	| `host` | `string` | - | The host address for the Restate server |
 70	| `port` | `number` | `9080` | The port number for the Restate server |
 71	| `propagateIncomingHeaders` | `true \| string[]` | `undefined` | Controls header propagation to downstream service calls |
